      "content": "it's just that people always say \"it gets better\" or \"stay strong,\" but they don't get it. they aren't the ones living in this. staying strong just feels like a way to prolong the torture. if i could just choose to have some actual stillness... wouldn't that be more compassionate than forcing someone to suffer indefinitely?",
